then I'm gonna kill myself."

05:12.573 --> 05:14.401
What do I do if--
- That is in here,

05:14.401 --> 05:15.619
because we do get that...

05:15.619 --> 05:17.447
Really quite a lot.

05:17.447 --> 05:19.623
