I looked unpolished,

06:08.759 --> 06:10.195
so you're kinda talking out
both sides of your mouth there.

06:11.414 --> 06:13.677
Oh, yeah.
My roots are really bad. Wow.

06:13.677 --> 06:15.331
Ooh, I could use some filler, too.

06:15.331 --> 06:16.332
I'm gonna go.

06:16.332 --> 06:17.855
Oh, my God.

06:17.855 --> 06:19.596
Hey, Dori.
Get Dr. Kazemi on the phone.

06:19.596 --> 06:21.468
