Jack's my grandson's name.

06:47.319 --> 06:49.539
- That's, uh, that's cool.
- You remind me of him.

06:49.539 --> 06:52.890
He's a good kid.
That's two good kids.

06:52.890 --> 06:54.414
So what can I do for you, Jack?

06:57.155 --> 06:58.156
- Syd.
- Yeah.

06:58.156 --> 06:59.767
- You've been a valuable--
- Oh!

06:59.767 --> 07:01.464
What size mitt do you wear?

07:01.464 --> 07:02.900
My mitt size?

07:02.900 --> 07:05.381
I've got an extra glove.
I think it might fit you.

07:05.381 --> 07:07.165
- Adult?
- Yeah, that'll work.

07:08.906 --> 07:09.907
Yeah.

07:12.257 --> 07:14.608
"Please know
that Payne greatly values

07:14.608 --> 07:16.087
