08:13.754 --> 08:15.582
Uh, "Take all
personal belongings with you

08:15.582 --> 08:18.541
as your card access
will be turned off."

08:18.541 --> 08:20.369
That sounds reasonable.
That's fine.

08:20.369 --> 08:22.240
Turn the page.

08:22.240 --> 08:23.764
Wait!
I'm fired?

08:23.764 --> 08:25.113
