to happen?

08:42.173 --> 08:43.610
"If they invoke God,

08:43.610 --> 08:45.525
maintain a neutral disposition,
and do not engage."

08:47.178 --> 08:49.224
I don't think
you're supposed to read that.

08:49.224 --> 08:54.185
"Once again, thank you
for your time and service."

08:54.185 --> 08:55.883
Howard?
Are you all right?

08:55.883 --> 08:57.058
I'm fine.

08:59.103 --> 09:00.583
"Excellent.

09:00.583 --> 09:04.065
I'm so happy we've come
to a satisfactory conclusion."

09:05.370 --> 09:07.634
Howard, are you sure
you're fine?

09:07.634 --> 09:09.636
I'm fine.

09:09.636 --> 09:11.551
"Excellent.

09:11.551 --> 09:13.640
I'm so happy we've come
to a satisfactory conclusion."

09:13.640 --> 09:16.164
Shall I--I tell you what,

09:16.164 --> 09:17.165
